<!-- Node: "DOOM 3 is shipping to the US stores" -->
<div class="body_box_header">DOOM 3 is shipping to the US stores</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Tuesday, August 3, 2004 - 12:50</small><br /><br />
Well it's the day DOOM 3 ships to the stores of US. People who preordered DOOM will be able to get it today, for others it'll be 4th or later. Some even got it earlier and you can see a bunch of new DOOM 3 screenshots around the net. Check back at RUST to see if we have any tutorials for you. Also visit our <a href = "http://forums.gamedesign.net/viewforum.php?f=50&sid=8484023e531aba35986a171f90db53d3">DOOM 3 Forum</a> or irc channel on irc.gamesurge.net entitled #rust to disscuss DOOM 3.
