<!-- Node: "Official DOOM 3 Hardware Guide" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Official DOOM 3 Hardware Guide</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Thursday, July 29, 2004 - 18:42</small><br /><br />
Hard|OCP has got the official DOOM 3 hardware guide, which tests a few video cards. They also test the newest nVidia and ATI video cards to see which one is better. Article include a few pictures comparing different video cards with different quality, resolution, etc. Head over to <a href = "http://www2.hardocp.com/article.html?art=NjQ0">Hard|OPC</a> for the guide.
