<div class="body_box_header">Kingpin: Final Crime released!!</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Monday, July 26, 2004 - 14:12</small><br /><br />
The project, which I was working on for 7 months is finally finished. Kingpin: Final Crime is unofficial sequel to Kingpin by Xatrix Entertainment, Inc. with new maps, characters, sounds and cutscenes. Here're some screenshots:<br><br>
<img src = "http://method.gamedesign.net/images/scrnshot/kingpin002_sm.gif">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src = "http://method.gamedesign.net/images/scrnshot/kingpin006_sm.gif"><br><br><img src = "http://method.gamedesign.net/images/scrnshot/kingpin013_sm.gif">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src = "http://method.gamedesign.net/images/scrnshot/kingpin017_sm.gif"><br><br>

